      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"\" \u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eDemand Forecasting Time-Series Analysis App\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n      This app performs exploratory time-series analysis on historical product sales data. It provides decomposition into trend, seasonality, and residual components, along with multiple visual insights at different aggregation levels. The goal is to uncover temporal patterns, seasonal cycles, and store/item-level sales behavior, which serve as a foundation for forecasting models.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Train-test split visualization for time-based modeling\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Seasonal decomposition (Observed, Trend, Seasonal, Residual)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Distribution analysis of sales values\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Temporal visualizations:\u003c/li\u003e\r\n     \r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e HTML/interactive Plotly outputs for insights delivery\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eKey Highlights\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cb\u003eTime-Series Features:\u003c/b\u003e Generates date-based features (day, month, year, week of year, weekend flag, etc.)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cb\u003eDecomposition:\u003c/b\u003e Identifies long-term trends, repeating seasonal cycles, and random residual noise using statsmodels seasonal decomposition\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cb\u003eEDA Insights\r\n      \u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cb\u003eVisualization:\u003c/b\u003e Provides interactive Plotly charts (line, histogram, boxplot) for deeper insights into demand patterns\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n",
